        "description": "Step into the immersive world of Very Real Pizza, a cutting-edge Virtual Reality game that offers a dynamic and engaging way to hone essential job skills. Take on the role of a pizza shop manager and navigate through a fast-paced environment. From meticulously crafting pizzas following complex recipes and customer preferences, to handling orders during busy rushes, you'll learn to master multitasking and stress management. The game simulates lifelike customer interactions, where you'll practice effective communication and problem-solving. As you progress, challenges escalate, testing your ability to adapt and excel under pressure. Whether you're a novice or a seasoned professional, Very Real Pizza provides an interactive platform to refine procedures, follow instructions, and thrive in a lifelike work setting. Get ready to top, bake, and deliver your way to success!",
